  },
  {
    "id": "4b902508-ab52-4bb5-b9f4-bd565edd48d9",
    "key": "google_reviews_data",
    "value": [
      {
        "text": "brought my car in with some scratches from scraping along some MDF baseboard trim, David cleaned it up with a 3-stage paint correction and blended it out, color-sanding to fill the scratches that went very deep - hardly noticeable now unless in just the right light and looking closely.  Also got a vinyl coating to protect from future abrasion for 6 months, feels smooth as glass!",
        "author": "William Chenoweth",
        "rating": 5,
        "relativeTime": "3 years ago"
      },
      {
        "text": "Detail shops are everywhere in the South Bay, and they even come to you now days — but they don’t have Dave and Segundo. I purchased the car of my dreams and didn’t know who to trust with my new baby, but after two phone calls with David, I’m so glad I chose Smart Details for my new car paint needs. David was incredibly patient and explained the full process of paint decontamination, polishing, the need to knows of ceramic coating, and much more. His expertise and passion for this type of work is unmatched and you couldn’t find a nicer place to work with. My new vehicle had full ceramic coating, paint correction and such, providing great protection from the elements. My car was done all in one day, with a through explanation of what to expect in the future. I’m super stoked to go back and purchase more supplies to upkeep my vehicle and will have all my detailing needs done here in the future without any hesitation ever. Thanks Smart Details, you rock!!!",
        "author": "Dusty Kramer",
        "rating": 5,
        "relativeTime": "3 years ago"
      },
      {
        "text": "Brought my track car in after a dusty season with a few offs, they did a great job getting the rubber marks and brake dust off 🌠. Didn't upsell me on anything, if anything I could've been convinced to spend more! Just means I'll come back sooner ;)",
        "author": "Jonathan Geisinger",
        "rating": 5,
        "relativeTime": "2 years ago"
      },
      {
        "text": "My car was nasty when I told David about it and I needed it asap. He said \"Give me your car keys and we'll take care of it\". OMG! When I got my car back, it was like I have never seen it before 🤩. My car was amazingly clean ✅. Thank you guys! Very professional car treatment and friendly service. 👍🏻",
        "author": "Reyna Ramirez",
        "rating": 5,
        "relativeTime": "3 years ago"
      },
      {
        "text": "I had an amazing experience with this interior detailing service! David was professional and friendly, the staff did an amazing job with the interior cleaning of my car. Every inch of my car's interior was meticulously cleaned and restored to perfection! I highly recommend their services for a flawless interior detail. Five stars all the way!",
        "author": "Kevin Martinez",
        "rating": 5,
        "relativeTime": "2 years ago"
      }
    ],
    "description": null,
    "updated_by": null,
    "created_at": "2026-02-16T22:00:02.398073+00:00",
    "updated_at": "2026-02-27T22:00:01.488782+00:00"
